<h3><a id="concepts" name="concepts"></a>1.
Concepts</h3>

<blockquote>
  
  <p>This project is designed to
have you create MySQL tables in your database, create a foreign key
constraint, implement PHP scripts, to query a table to
authenticate users and insert records in a second table for session
control. You will learn these
concepts:</p>

  
  <ul>

    <li>Do CREATE TABLE and ALTER TABLE queries on
a
MySQL database<br />

    </li>

    <li>Use PHP
code to query user records in a table</li>
    <li>Authenticate users with an encrypted password</li>

    <li>Use
PHP code to save session information in a table and use it for authentication<br />

    </li>

  
  </ul>

</blockquote>

